material.content: {"text":"3. (Kofir) Inson Bizni uning suyaklarini jamlab olmas, deb o`ylarmi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,68]}]}

{"text":"4. Albatta, Biz uning barmoq uchlarini ham asl holiga keltirishga qodirmiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,75]}]}

{"text":"5. Balki, inson kelajakda fisqu fujur qilishni xohlaydir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,57]}]}
material.text: 5. Balki, inson kelajakda fisqu fujur qilishni xohlaydir.

material.content: {"text":"10. O`shal kunda inson: «Qochar joy qayerda?» deb qoladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,58]}]}

{"text":"13. U kunda insonga avvalu oxir qilgan ishlarining xabari beriladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,68]}]}

{"text":"14. Ha, inson o`z nafsiga qarshi o`zi shohiddir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,48]}]}

{"text":"17. Albatta, u(Qur'on)ni jamlash va o`qib berish Bizning zimmamizda.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,68]}]}

{"text":"18. Bas, Biz uni o`qisak, qiroatiga zehn solib tur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,51]}]}

{"text":"19. So`ngra u(Qur'on)ni bayon qilib berish ham Bizning zimmamizda.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,66]}]}

{"text":"24. Va u kunda tirishib-burishgan yuzlar ham bor.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,49]}]}

{"text":"32. Va lekin yolg`onga chiqardi va yuz o`girdi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,47]}]}

{"text":"35. Yana holingga voy bo`lsin sening, voy bo`lsin!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,50]}]}

{"text":"39. Bas, undan juftni — erkak va ayolni yaratdi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,48]}]}

{"text":"أَيَحْسَبُ ٱلْإِنسَٰنُ أَلَّن نَّجْمَعَ عِظَامَهُۥ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,50]}]}

{"text":"بَلَىٰ قَٰدِرِينَ عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّسَوِّىَ بَنَانَهُۥ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,51]}]}

{"text":"بَلْ يُرِيدُ ٱلْإِنسَٰنُ لِيَفْجُرَ أَمَامَهُۥ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,46]}]}

{"text":"يَقُولُ ٱلْإِنسَٰنُ يَوْمَئِذٍ أَيْنَ ٱلْمَفَرُّ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,48]}]}

{"text":"يُنَبَّؤُا۟ ٱلْإِنسَٰنُ يَوْمَئِذٍۭ بِمَا قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,59]}]}

{"text":"بَلِ ٱلْإِنسَٰنُ عَلَىٰ نَفْسِهِۦ بَصِيرَةٌۭ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,44]}]}

{"text":"لَا تُحَرِّكْ بِهِۦ لِسَانَكَ لِتَعْجَلَ بِهِۦٓ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,47]}]}

{"text":"تَظُنُّ أَن يُفْعَلَ بِهَا فَاقِرَةٌۭ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,37]}]}

{"text":"ثُمَّ ذَهَبَ إِلَىٰٓ أَهْلِهِۦ يَتَمَطَّىٰٓ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,43]}]}

{"text":"أَيَحْسَبُ ٱلْإِنسَٰنُ أَن يُتْرَكَ سُدًى","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,41]}]}

{"text":"أَلَمْ يَكُ نُطْفَةًۭ مِّن مَّنِىٍّۢ يُمْنَىٰ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,45]}]}

{"text":"ثُمَّ كَانَ عَلَقَةًۭ فَخَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,40]}]}

{"text":"فَجَعَلَ مِنْهُ ٱلزَّوْجَيْنِ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلْأُنثَىٰٓ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,53]}]}

{"text":"أَلَيْسَ ذَٰلِكَ بِقَٰدِرٍ عَلَىٰٓ أَن يُحْۦِىَ ٱلْمَوْتَىٰ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,59]}]}

{"text":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,0.74901962280273438,0.45098039507865906]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":14,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,40]}]}
